'''Zinedine Zidane''' (23 Kamena 1972, izina mu [[cyarabu]]: زين الدين يزيد زيدان) ni umukinnyi w'umufaransa wagacishijeho mu mu mupira w'amaguru, wakinaga nka no 10 mu kibuga mu ikipe y'igihugu y'ubufaransa akaba yaraciye mu makipe nka [[AS Cannes|Cannes]], [[FC Girondins de Bordeaux|Bordeaux]], [[Juventus F.C.|Juventus]] na Real Madrid ubu abereye umutoza. yatowe nk'umukinnyi mwiza ku mugabane w'uburayi na [[UEFA Golden Jubilee Poll]] mu myaka mirongo itanu ishize. yakinnye umukino wa mbere mu ikipe y'igihugu taliki ya 17 kanama 1994, mu mukino wa gicuti wahuzaga France na  [[Czech Republic national football team|Czech Republic]] aho yinjiye mu kibuga asimbura agafasha ikipe ye kunganya ibitego 2-2 nyumo yo gutsinda ibitego bibire wenyine.

